{
  "stem": "20088.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, I can wipe my bottom now with paper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was kind of a for building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was all with bits of glass.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was kind of insulation material, covered in glass splinters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you can imagine I was completely bleeding, and sore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was my experience with my bit of toilet paper, I thought.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody ever-- that was another peculiar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody ever got a period in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the minute you got in, you didn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said there was some bromide, which was supposed to be in the bread and in the liquid.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was what they told us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know if it's true.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And while we were in the work commando, we had one of-- a great miracle happened.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One day, I got a boil on my neck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was really very, very painful, and awful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was sort of-- there was a hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it wasn't really a hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was where Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Mengele worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he did his experiments there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And people did-- were put in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But practically nobody ever came out of it, because when you were ill, you know, you were really no use.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And you were selected out there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So nobody really wanted to go into hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I had this diarrhea and I got ill, all the people in my bunk said that you must go to hospital.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, no, I don't want to go, because then I won't come out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they kind of kept me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was very, very ill.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But with this boil, I said, I have to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was so out of a surgery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could go if you wanted something.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
